##The writing on these Hazmat suits, it's got ta be the first one

The papernews

The function introduction, has the connotation the current politics new media

This is a comprehensive report by thepaper.cn

Since the outbreak of the new crown, in order to facilitate communication, medical staff in the back to write their names, each other cheer.

The writing on these suits is like a vow of silence.

We can not see your faces, but we can see hope in these words.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
"I am here to treat the sick, to fight until I reach my goal, " said academician Li Lanjuan, 73.

"I am a party member, I went to Florida first" many health care workers, in addition to the name, but also the special mark these two words, this is a responsibility, a responsibility.

"It is a duty not to retreat, " Harvard Medical School's Wu Yiying helped Wuhan Golden Lake Hospital.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
"It's a lucky thing to be born in China, and you can't hold back when you are in danger, " said Xu Hanbing, a young man from 1995 who works as a nurse in four hospitals in Wuhan.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
"As long as we work together, we are really not far from winning the battle against the epidemic, " said Yi Junfeng, a 98-year-old male nurse, with colleagues Zhang Yao (center) and Yang Caixia (right) , intensive-care unit, Department of Neurology, Hunan Provincial People's Hospital, on February 7,2020. Although there is a risk of infection, but Yi Junfeng said, do not be afraid to do a good job of protection, male nurses are energetic, have a strong sense of the ability to fight the epidemic in the front-line advantage. Xinhua map

"everyone who does their best to care for their patients on the Internet will make them feel moved and empowered! It's powerful! " -- From around 21:00 on January 23, Florida sent her first tweet asking for help, wu Kang@bigwugod  , a 25 year old recovering from new crown pneumonia, posted more than 50 tweets, and his followers have grown from 1,000 to 1.79 million. These micro-blogs recorded his helplessness from the onset of hospitalization, suffering from illness, the warmth of the company of relatives and friends, the dedication of medical care and patient diagnosis and treatment, the feeling of being encouraged by netizens and the joy of recovery from the hospital.

Before BIGWUGOD  was released from the hospital, she saw the name of a sister nurse, which read "hope" in reverse, and "hope" written on her protective suit. "The steadfastness of their staff gives us, as patients, hope, " he said

Notes by BIGWUGOD  : On the 9th, a sister of a nurse's protective clothing said, "I'm here! Thor! " And it was said that Thor Mountain was ready to start taking patients, more and more people will be treated and the situation will be better and better. I hope the turning point will come soon.

During BIGWUGOD's hospital stay, one nurse wrote "All right" on her back, signifying that everything was fine, while another injected sister wrote "Sunny" on the back of her protective suit, explaining that she felt the epidemic had lasted so long, i think it's time to clear up.

Because after putting on the protective clothing to see clearly the face, everybody is the same, in order to facilitate the communication, the medical staff writes the name on the back, encourages each other.

"The winter in Wuhan is not cold at all this year because of our warm-blooded young people! "  Xu Yun, a mother of 90 and a second child in Shanghai Oriental Hospital, supports the ICU in Golden Pool Hospital

The medical staff of the shelter hospital marked themselves with "Zhou Black Duck" and "hot and dry surface" on the protective clothing.

"Little Love in Su, great love in Wu" -- Medical Team of the First Affiliated Hospital of Suzhou University

Zhu Rui, a male nurse at the first hospital in Fuzhou, who is helping Wuhan fight the epidemic, confessed to his girlfriend on a protective suit: I'll marry you when the epidemic is over.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Writing the love for distant family members on the protective clothing also brings patients the encouragement of love  The "special creativity" of the First Affiliated Hospital of Suzhou University and the First Hospital of Nanjing City supporting the health care workers in Hubei Province.

At Wuhan Jinyintan Hospital, medical staff of the Shanghai medical team wrote their names and words of encouragement on their protective clothing.

These direct and affectionate words, is the 14th before starting work, is the first hospital in Nanjing to support Hubei Medical Workers "special creativity. ".

His wife is from Tianmen in Hubei Province, and the military doctor said he is half from Hubei Province. When a family member gets sick, you do your best.

To facilitate identification, the eight young "war disease" commandos from the three Zhongshan Hospitals supporting the Hankou Hospital wrote their names on the protective clothing: Good Luck, good luck, peace, joy, Wing Wah, wealth, fortune, treasure. The cause is a member of the team called auspicious, we follow the train of thought, using auspicious words to name. Captain Duan Mengqi said he hoped to bring good mood to patients and teammates.

"I cut the new crown, carry you to appreciate the Cherry" , the medical staff will write the oath on the protective clothing.

I hope you're the brightest star in the night. At Wuhan Jinyintan Hospital, Jiang Huijia, from Shanghai's Fengxian District Central Hospital, wrote her name and words of encouragement on her protective clothing.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Medical staff at the Naval Medical University write their names on protective clothing for identification.

A nurse in Wuhan, China, who carries a lantern, posted a picture of herself writing "Hu Ge's wife" on her protective clothing, saying she hoped it would help ease the heavy atmosphere in the ward. "You are the most beautiful little bald head, I hope the epidemic will be over soon, and I hope your 'hijab' will be lifted soon, " wrote@Hu GE on Weibo on Thursday. "You can borrow this name for a while, and please return it to me later. " Look forward to raising your hijab to the top of the Popular Weibo Search.
